<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;The Walker&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Move from the back of the class (where the Secretary is) to the front where the printouts of the text are and they read the text&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Memorize a small portion of the text and walks back to the Secretary&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Secretary&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Write down as the Walker dictates what they memorized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Walker&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Make sure the homophones and grammar rules are written correctly by the Secretary&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
